reviews.content: The seats are clean and cozy in winter, the owner is quick and enthusiastic with customers. The restaurant has many delicious dishes, especially the porridge hotpot that makes you sober up...
The restaurant is quite famous among office drinkers, located at 15 Ly Thai To, Hoan Kiem, Hanoi. …
Delicious everyone, very discreet, recommend everyone to try steamed snails, porridge hotpot, nem thinh, snail sausage.
Space is a bit tight but food is good and prices are reasonable. Parking is convenient.
A casual eatery with a rustic design. The food consists of traditional dishes, all well-prepared and delicious, with a few unique items. Prices are a bit high.
Ate twice, food was quite good, food came out a bit slow, seats were a bit cramped, suitable for winter
The food is delicious but the family service is a bit slow and the restaurant is crowded.
Delicious restaurant, I've eaten there several times, the pig cheek porridge is very delicious, ok restaurant
